### Multi-q SDMA AG implemented (Entry 40)

`MORI_MULTI_Q_AG=1` distributes AG chunks over qId `1 + c % min(numQ-1,15)`
instead of serializing all chunks on qId=1. Host tracks per-q AG generation
counters to avoid unsafe signal resets. Default path unchanged. This targets
the ~1ms AG wait seen in continuous phase timing.

